The other case; $\int_{-\pi^{\frac{1}{n}}}^{\pi^{\frac{1}{n}}}\left(\frac{\sin\left(x^{n}\right)}{x^{n}}\right)dx$
can be solved with a simple u sub (of $x^n$) and then integration by parts
